import styled from "styled-components"
import Adds from "../comps/Adds"
import Footer from "../comps/Footer"
import Navbar from "../comps/Navbar"

const Container = styled.div``

const Cart = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
        <Navbar/>
        <Adds/>
        <Wrapper>
            <Title>Your bag</Title>
            <Top></Top>
            <Bottom></Bottom>
        </Wrapper>
        <Footer/>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Cart
